 without affecting the URL.\\n*   **`src/components/`**: Organized by scope:\\n    *   `ui/`: Base primitives (shadcn/ui).\\n    *   `global/`: App-wide UI (Navbar, Footer).\\n    *   `common/`: Shared utilities (Spinners, Containers).\\n    *   `[domain]/`: Feature-specific components (e.g., `shop/`, `auth/`).\\n*   **`src/services/`**: The **Service Layer** for all external API calls (Supabase, Stripe, WooCommerce). Logic stays here, not in the components.\\n*   **`src/store/`**: Centralized state management using **Zustand**.\\n*   **`src/lib/`**: Shared utilities and third-party client initializations (e.g., Stripe/Supabase clients).\\n*   **`src/types/`**: Centralized TypeScript definitions and re-exports.\\n\\n### **Recommended Next Step**\\nWhen we move to implementation for Factory V2, we should initialize the repository using this exact scaffolding to ensure alignment with the Stark Software Factory standards.\\n\\n### **Action Checklist (Done looks like)**\\n*   [ ] **Root:** `src/` folder exists and contains all application code.\\n*   [ ] **Routing:** `app/` uses route groups `(public)` and `(auth)` as the baseline.\\n*   [ ] **Components:** `components/ui` is reserved for primitives; feature code is strictly domain-grouped.\\n*   [ ] **Logic:** No direct `fetch` calls in components; all data fetching is moved to `services/`.\\n\\nReady to proceed with the `FACTORY_V2_APP_BRIEF`, or do you want to dive deeper into a specific part of the folder spec?\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":\"adk-1c24b6f5-f646-49f7-bcba-7f598af25a7f\",\"args\":{\"skill_name\":\"SESSION_MEMORY_SKILL\"},\"name\":\"invoke_skill\"},{\"id\":\"adk-612d23de-1024-4bf2-af1f-97878ff50708\",\"args\":{\"days\":7},\"name\":\"read_session_memory\"},{\"id\":\"adk-283ab1ff-997e-466b-ada5-9ec8a168c218\",\"args\":{\"doc_name\":\"APP_ARCHITECTURE_MANUAL\"},\"name\":\"read_context_doc\"}],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"expected_invoc